  "3300760": {
    "name": "掠宝法师 (LootMage)",
    "steam_appid": 3300760,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LootMage</strong> 是一款以中世纪奇幻世界为背景的 <strong>弹幕射击动作 Roguelite</strong> 游戏。<br>在这个世界中，你将扮演一位冒险者，踏入不断变化的地牢，与各种敌人激战，收集宝物，并全力求生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >魔法点缀的弹幕射击动作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/c4cad1b41cbfb60d4746ad9d1f5b6bf7.poster.avif?t=1771652322\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/c4cad1b41cbfb60d4746ad9d1f5b6bf7.webm?t=1771652322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/c4cad1b41cbfb60d4746ad9d1f5b6bf7.mp4?t=1771652322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对敌人毫不留情的弹幕攻击，你需要灵活躲避，并运用强大的魔法来体验惊险刺激的战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦失败，你会失去所有道具，但在此过程中累积的技能与经验，将成为你下一次挑战的强大助力。<br>你能否一路闯到地牢的最深处呢？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化的武器与道具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/629902aec2bb766da2332a9a4faa6679.poster.avif?t=1771652322\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/629902aec2bb766da2332a9a4faa6679.webm?t=1771652322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个世界里，存在魔法杖、沉重巨剑、魔法球体等多种多样的武器和道具。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地牢中能够找到什么、又如何组合并运用这些物品继续冒险，全看你的运气与选择。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >道具协同系统</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有被动道具都蕴含着两种不同的魔法精华。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集2个、4个或6个拥有相同精华的道具，可以激活特殊的协同效果。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >弹幕自定义系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/921badb703f6b3cf61be053e7710a317.poster.avif?t=1771652322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/921badb703f6b3cf61be053e7710a317.webm?t=1771652322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/921badb703f6b3cf61be053e7710a317.mp4?t=1771652322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔力石蕴含着强大的魔法能量。护臂是一种能引导这种力量的特殊装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用魔力石激活秘印，可以强化或改变你的战斗能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组合各种弹幕选项，打造属于自己的战斗风格！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无法预测的地牢</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/67b56ce43835bddcc594206e0c30acea.poster.avif?t=1771652322\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/67b56ce43835bddcc594206e0c30acea.webm?t=1771652322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300760/extras/67b56ce43835bddcc594206e0c30acea.mp4?t=1771652322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次进入地牢，都是全新的、由程序生成的关卡，充满不可预测的挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在似曾相识却又不同的环境中，不断摸索敌人的攻击模式和地形特色，一步步提升自己的实力。<br>也许用不了多久，你就能在这个地牢中磨炼出适应生存的本能。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「在 <strong>LootMage 的地牢中， </strong><br>永远都有全新的宝藏与挑战在等待着你。」</p>",
